                                <td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=11224&amp;sid=cfacca5b1fcbd37cafc8d90621c7f9af#11224"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Dec 02, 2003 4:14 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Charm XP Rules - Explain?</span></td>
                                <td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=11224&amp;sid=cfacca5b1fcbd37cafc8d90621c7f9af"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
