                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">the EQLive link is WRONG for charmed pets.
<br />
Kadath has it correct for solo/group.
<br />

<br />
Proving EQlive link wrong is quite easy -- kill a mob with your pet, doing one point of damage, observe how much exp you gain.
<br />

<br />
Now, get a mob down to ~2% and let your pet die.  Then nuke the mob to death.  Notice the large difference in EXP gained.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Eleandra
