                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">neat little trick i tried out to void exp loss...but it can become a pain in the butt heh
<br />

<br />
1) pull with tash
<br />
2) get snared (if your duo with snarer)
<br />
3) Haste pet (i know a lot of people dont like doing this but its necisary)
<br />
4) /pet guard here
<br />
5) break charm and root mob
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Next mobs</span>
<br />
1) pull tash
<br />
2) <span style="font-weight: bold">SLOW</span>
<br />
3) charm slowed mob
<br />
4) sick it on rooted hasted mob
<br />
5) when charm mob gets low break charm and finish off
<br />

<br />
the only exp you loose this way is for the rooted mob :/ but its a pain to get working specially cuz root is even more random then charm</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />[65 Coercer] <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=459722" target="_blank" class="postlink"> Aertea Neuroflux</a> <a href="http://divinecrusade.org" target="_blank" class="postlink">&lt;Divine Crusade&gt;</a> Tunare Server - EQ
