                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mana spent directly correlates to downtime, which is time you're not getting xp.  Therefore, for any tactic for getting 100% xp to be worth it, it would have to take no more than 1.5 times as much mana/time as the ole Ceramic Band method (100 is 1.5 times 67).
<br />

<br />
Most ideas I've heard would take more than 1.5 times as much time (total of extra time spent + time to regen extra mana spent).
<br />

<br />
Anyways, we can kill things so quickly that even with a 33% penalty it's better than most folks can do solo.
<br />

<br />
