                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I don't haste or slow anything during charm kiting.  This is for when I don't want to keep a pet for more than 1 fight, which is 99% of the time for me.  I'd rather burn thru as many mobs as possible (including my pets).
<br />

<br />
Pac pair of mobs
<br />
Tash first
<br />
Druid snares him on inc~
<br />
Charm him
<br />
Tash second mob
<br />
Druid snares on inc
<br />
/Pet attack
<br />

<br />
med for few seconds
<br />

<br />
Dispell charm when target mob under 1 bub.
<br />

<br />
Nuke both mobs down (they should be at same health, it's not hard to keep them even).
<br />

<br />
Rinse repeat~
<br />

<br />

<br />
-Ruserious-</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
