                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The ring requires you to equip it, and target yourself and then tab switch after you break charm. It's definitely worth it though since you can root immediately with no gem refresh. 
<br />

<br />
Boots of the Mosquito are clickable from inventory, but are much harder to find and clearly self only. Both have the effect "invisibility to animals" which works well, and it's nice when running away to zone in tactics if you have to since the boars and birds are animals and won't see you. Sort of a perk if you're exping there.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />When I was young I used to pray to God that He would give me a new bicycle. I soon found out that God didn't work that way, so I stole a bike and asked Him to forgive me.
<br />

<br />
E65.207/7H h-- 3.1Khp ft9 !g e+++ o+ T-- H++(+++) c++ t+ X--</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
